history.content: I'm taking 162 with 176 and Data 144 in the Fall.  I unfortunately lost my internship this summer, so I'm 20-hr TA'ing and taking a class (tentatively 188) for the summer.  Will 169 and 162 and recruiting take up too much time?  I am/was hoping someone could somehow say that 169 makes up for the internship.  Or I could just drop 188 and take that in the Fall instead if this isn’t feasible.  This is my last year and I'm pretty much out of "mainstream" CS classes to take other than 189 with Shewchuk in the Spring.  I'm used to taking 3 and 4 hard technicals a semester FWIW.
